Package org.apache.http.impl.auth

Interface SpnegoTokenGenerator

  • @Deprecated
public interface SpnegoTokenGenerator
    Deprecated.
    (4.2) subclass KerberosScheme and override GGSSchemeBase.generateGSSToken(byte[], org.ietf.jgss.Oid, String, org.apache.http.auth.Credentials)
    Abstract SPNEGO token generator. Implementations should take an Kerberos ticket and transform into a SPNEGO token.

    Implementations of this interface are expected to be thread-safe.
